b'{"data_headers":{"result_code":1},"data":{"information":{"article_id":2829,"category_name":"News","pr_category_id":"1","title_name":"Gala Dragalia Remix Is Now Live!","message":"<div>Gala Dragalia Remix started on <span class=\\"local_date\\" data-local_date=\\"1644818400\\"><\/span>!<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>\\u25a0What Are Gala Dragalia and Gala Dragalia Remix?<\/div><div>The initial appearance rate for 5\\u2605 adventurers and dragons is boosted to 6%, which is up from the standard 4%! If you get a 5\\u2605 summon or 5\\u2605 featured summon, the appearance rate will return to the initial 6%.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div><span style=\\"color: rgb(226, 80, 65);\\">The newly added 5\\u2605 adventurer Nina (wind) will also appear in subsequent summon showcases.<\/span><\/div><div><span style=\\"color: rgb(226, 80, 65);\\"><br><\/span><\/div><div><span style=\\"color: rgb(226, 80, 65);\\">Dragons added in past Gala Dragalia summon showcases may appear in this summon showcase as well. For information about which dragons may appear, tap Summon on the in-game footer menu, then select Appearance Rates and check the Appearance Rates section.<\/span><\/div><div><br><\/div><div>\\u25bcNewly added featured adventurer:<\/div><div>5\\u2605 Nina (wind\/staff)<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>\\u25bcFeatured dragon from past Gala Dragalia summon showcases:<\/div><div>5\\u2605 Gala Reborn Zephyr (wind)<\/div><div><br><\/div><div><span style=\\"color: rgb(226, 80, 65);\\">In this summon showcase, the following limited-time adventurers make their return but are not featured.<\/span><\/div><div><br><\/div><div>Returning limited-time adventurers:<\/div><div>5\\u2605 Valentine&#39;s Chelsea (wind\/bow)<\/div><div>5\\u2605 Valentine&#39;s Melody (wind\/axe)<\/div><div>5\\u2605 Valentine&#39;s Addis (shadow\/bow)<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>Gala Dragalia Remix appearance rates:<\/div><div>5\\u2605 total: 6.00%<\/div><div>5\\u2605 featured total: 1.30% (Adventurers: 0.50%, Dragons: 0.80%)<\/div><div>5\\u2605 standard total: 4.70% (Adventurers: 2.50%, Dragons: 2.20%)<\/div><div>4\\u2605 standard total: 16.00% (Adventurers: 8.55%, Dragons: 7.45%)<\/div><div>3\\u2605 standard total: 78.00% (Adventurers: 47.00%, Dragons: 31.00%)<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>Gala Dragalia Remix event duration:<\/div><div><span class=\\"local_date\\" data-local_date=\\"1644818400\\"><\/span> to <span class=\\"local_date\\" data-local_date=\\"1645077599\\"><\/span><\/div><div><br><\/div><div>Get a closer look at the featured adventurer and dragon below.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>Featured adventurer:<\/div><div>\\n<div class=\\"summonPickUp\\">\\n<div class=\\"imageStatusWrap\\">\\n\\t<div class=\\"mainImage\\"><img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/aa28cb8ae0db49821c0731a6451aa886.png\\"><\/div>\\n\\t<div class=\\"status\\">\\n\\t\\t<div class=\\"title\\">Stats<\/div>\\n\\t\\t<div class=\\"param\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t<div class=\\"base\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<ul>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<li class=\\"lv\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<span>Lv<\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<span>80<\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<\/li><li class=\\"type\\"><img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/1fc4080420e16a67744809f28590c98b2.png\\"><\/li>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<li class=\\"skill\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<span>10<\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<\/li>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<\/ul>\\n\\t\\t\\t<\/div>\\n\\t\\t\\t<div class=\\"base under\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<ul>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<li class=\\"hp\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<span>HP<\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<span>807<\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<\/li>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<li class=\\"atk\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<span>Strength<\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<span>468<\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<\/li>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<\/ul>\\n\\t\\t\\t<\/div>\\n            <div class=\\"lower-area\\">\\n                <div class=\\"total\\">\\n                    <span><img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/a8a2cd128481266e95fd4fbbbac90fbd2.png\\" alt=\\"\\"><\/span>\\n                    <span>2,515<\/span>\\n                <\/div>\\n            <\/div>\\n        <\/div>\\n\\t\\t\\t<div class=\\"status\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<div class=\\"title\\">Adventurer Details<\/div>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<div class=\\"param\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<ul>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<li>A bright and cheerful woman who runs a shop in<br>South Grastaea. She earnestly serves any<br>customer who comes her way, but is merciless<br>when it comes to shoplifters or those who make<br>unreasonable demands.<\/li>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<\/ul>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<\/div>\\n\\t\\t\\t<\/div>\\n\\t\\t<\/div><\/div><div class=\\"skill explanation\\">\\n\\t<div class=\\"title\\">Skills<\/div>\\n\\t<dl><dt class=\\"skill-cost-wrap\\"\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<span><img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/febed52c0bbb22852312ef8a69f450cb2.png\\"><\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<span>Pop-up Shop<\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<div class=\\"skill-cost\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<span>Shareable<\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<div class=\\"txt-num\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<span>6<\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<\/div>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<\/div>\\n\\t\\t\\t<\/dt>\\n\\t\\t\\t<dd><div>Restores HP to all teammates. This recovery is<br>increased to ten times its normal potency for<br>teammates who are at 30% of their maximum HP<br>or less. Then, gradually recovers the entire team\'s<br>HP.<br><br>In addition, activates the following cumulative<br>effects based on the number of charges the<br>shopkeeper gauge has.<br><br>One or more: This skill\'s recovery potency is<br>increased.<br>Two or more: Removes all afflictions from the<br>entire team.<br>Three: Grants the entire team a team strength amp.<\/div><div class=\\"skill-detail\\"><color=#00008B>Shopkeeper Gauge = 0 Charge(s):<\/color><br>Recovery Potency: 10<br>Skill Energy Required: 5,916<br>Skill Energy Required (Shared Skill): 9,169<br>Special Effects:<br>\\u30fbHP Regen<br>\\u3000\\u3000Lasts 40 seconds<br>\\u3000\\u3000Triggers every 2.9 seconds<br>\\u3000\\u3000Potency: 25<br><br><color=#00008B>Shopkeeper Gauge = 1 Charge(s):<\/color><br>Recovery Potency: 21<br>Special Effects:<br>\\u30fbHP Regen<br>\\u3000\\u3000Lasts 40 seconds<br>\\u3000\\u3000Triggers every 2.9 seconds<br>\\u3000\\u3000Potency: 25<br><br><color=#00008B>Shopkeeper Gauge = 2 Charge(s):<\/color><br>Recovery Potency: 21<br>Special Effects:<br>\\u30fbHP Regen<br>\\u3000\\u3000Lasts 40 seconds<br>\\u3000\\u3000Triggers every 2.9 seconds<br>\\u3000\\u3000Potency: 25<br>\\u30fbAffliction Recovery (All Afflictions)<br><br><color=#00008B>Shopkeeper Gauge = 3 Charge(s):<\/color><br>Recovery Potency: 21<br>Special Effects:<br>\\u30fbHP Regen<br>\\u3000\\u3000Lasts 40 seconds<br>\\u3000\\u3000Triggers every 2.9 seconds<br>\\u3000\\u3000Potency: 25<br>\\u30fbAffliction Recovery (All Afflictions)<br>Team Amps:<br>\\u30fbStrength Amp (MAX Lv. = 1)<\/div><\/dd><dt\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<span><img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/275a89229a56fc552cb6eaa8508951262.png\\"><\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<span>Everything Must Go!<\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t<\/dt>\\n\\t\\t\\t<dd><div>This skill can only be used when the<br>shopkeeper gauge is completely filled.<br><br>Completely consumes the shopkeeper gauge,<br>revives any incapacitated teammates, and<br>completely restores their HP. Also, restores HP<br>to all teammates and removes all afflictions<br>from the entire team.<br><br>Furthermore, partially fills the skill gauges of all<br>teammates, excluding the user and dragons.<br>During this skill, the user will be immune to<br>knockback.<\/div><div class=\\"skill-detail\\">Recovery Potency: 300<br>Skill Energy Required: 8,352<br>Special Effects:<br>\\u30fbRevival<br>\\u30fbRecovered from Afflictions<br>\\u30fbSkill Prep<br>\\u3000\\u3000Potency: 100%<\/div><\/dd><\/dl><\/div>\\n\\t<div class=\\"exAbility explanation\\">\\n\\t\\t<div class=\\"title\\">Co-ability<\/div>\\n\\t\\t<dl>\\n\\t\\t\\t<dt>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<span><img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/799d30d618475a89802dad3d29b6ca252.png\\"><\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<span>Recovery Potency +20%<\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t<\/dt>\\n\\t\\t\\t<dd>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<div>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\tIncreases the potency of recovery skills by 20%.<br>Benefits your whole team.\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<\/div>\\n\\t\\t\\t<\/dd>\\n\\t\\t<\/dl>\\n\\t<\/div>\\n\\n\\t<div class=\\"exAbility explanation\\">\\n\\t\\t<div class=\\"title\\">Chain Co-ability<\/div>\\n\\t\\t<dl>\\n\\t\\t\\t<dt>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<span><img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/368330649dd4e9c07abc8582ae510ece2.png\\"><\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<span>(Wind) Team Strength Amp = HP Regen V<\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t<\/dt>\\n\\t\\t\\t<dd>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<div>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\tIf a team member is attuned to Wind:<br>gradually recovers their HP when they<br>have a team strength amp.<br>Benefits your whole team.\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<\/div>\\n\\t\\t\\t<\/dd>\\n\\t\\t<\/dl>\\n\\t<\/div>\\n<div class=\\"ability explanation\\">\\n\\t<div class=\\"title\\">Abilities<\/div>\\n\\t<dl><dt><span><img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/cabfd8229c6af11c5b1f4e6ea9115ed42.png\\"><\/span><span>Sharp Shopkeeping II<\/span><\/dt><dd><div>Grants the user a shopkeeper gauge that has<br>three charges and is completely filled at the<br>start of quests. The shopkeeper gauge is filled<br>by using Pop-up Shop.<br><br>Also, grants the user a unique force strike that<br>deals damage to the target and nearby enemies.<br>When the shopkeeper gauge has one or more<br>charges, this force strike will also dispel enemy<br>buffs.<\/div><\/dd><dt><span><img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/42aad01fa9cb510052712a9ef6882f4b2.png\\"><\/span><span>Freeze Res +100%<\/span><\/dt><dd><div>Reduces susceptibility to freezing by 100%.<\/div><\/dd><dt><span><img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/77e6a5d022e8d9cc368641382287ea682.png\\"><\/span><span>Ceaseless Sales II<\/span><\/dt><dd><div>Grants Pop-up Shop a skill gauge attached<br>to its skill button.<br><br>When the shopkeeper gauge has one or more<br>charges, Pop-up Shop can be used even if its<br>skill gauge is not filled. Using Pop-up Shop in<br>this way will consume one charge of the<br>shopkeeper gauge.<br><br>Also, consuming one or more charges of the<br>shopkeeper gauge will grant the entire team<br>a team strength amp with a maximum team amp<br>level of one. After this amp is granted, this ability<br>will not grant it again for 45 seconds.<\/div><\/dd><\/dl><\/div><\/div><\/div><div><br><\/div><div>\\u30fbThe stats shown here do not include increases or decreases due to abilities and represent the adventurer at level 80 with 50 mana nodes unlocked, not the stats when first obtained.<\/div><div>\\u30fbSome skills have different effects when used as a shared skill.<\/div><div>Note: Please see the in-game Help section for further details on the skill effect that revives incapacitated teammates.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>Featured dragon:<\/div><div>\\n<div class=\\"summonPickUp\\">\\n<div class=\\"imageStatusWrap\\">\\n\\t<div class=\\"mainImage\\"><img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/ab4960d508720739de1a856c948dc01f.png\\"><\/div>\\n\\t<div class=\\"status\\">\\n\\t\\t<div class=\\"title\\">Stats<\/div>\\n\\t\\t<div class=\\"param\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t<div class=\\"base\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<ul>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<li class=\\"lv\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<span>Lv<\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<span>100<\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<\/li>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<\/ul>\\n\\t\\t\\t<\/div>\\n\\t\\t\\t<div class=\\"base under\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<ul>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<li class=\\"hp\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<span>HP<\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<span>369<\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<\/li>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<li class=\\"atk\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<span>Strength<\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<span>126<\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<\/li>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<\/ul>\\n\\t\\t\\t<\/div>\\n            <div class=\\"lower-area\\">\\n                <div class=\\"total\\">\\n                    <span><img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/a8a2cd128481266e95fd4fbbbac90fbd2.png\\" alt=\\"\\"><\/span>\\n                    <span>1,295<\/span>\\n                <\/div>\\n            <\/div>\\n        <\/div>\\n\\t\\t\\t<div class=\\"status\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<div class=\\"title\\">Dragon Details<\/div>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<div class=\\"param\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<ul>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<li>Through the belief of the people of the plains,<br>Zephyr has been reborn. Freed from the noxious<br>miasma eating away at his body, his prudence is<br>now tempered with an unwavering will and an<br>open mind.<\/li>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<\/ul>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<\/div>\\n\\t\\t\\t<\/div>\\n\\t\\t<\/div><\/div><div class=\\"skill explanation\\">\\n\\t<div class=\\"title\\">Skills<\/div>\\n\\t<dl><dt\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<span><img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/930e79020344385658dbc5220432cb572.png\\"><\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<span>Howling Fury<\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t<\/dt>\\n\\t\\t\\t<dd><div>Deals damage to the target and nearby enemies.<br>If the user is targeting an enemy and not using a<br>skill when their remaining shapeshift time runs out,<br>this skill will be used automatically, regardless of<br>whether or not the skill gauge is filled.<\/div><div class=\\"skill-detail\\">Damage: 1,923 \\u00d7 1 hit<br><\/div><\/dd><\/dl><\/div><div class=\\"ability explanation\\">\\n\\t<div class=\\"title\\">Abilities<\/div>\\n\\t<dl><dt><span><img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/87595b7438e74e5502d8b830d6bd16832.png\\"><\/span><span>(Wind) Strength +70%<\/span><\/dt><dd><div>If the user is attuned to Wind: <br>increases strength by 70%.<\/div><\/dd><dt><span><img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/65863989132db80658f5d919573c14e92.png\\"><\/span><span>(Wind) Wrath of the Plains II<\/span><\/dt><dd><div>If the user is attuned to Wind:<br>adds 30% to the modifier applied to damage<br>against water-attuned enemies and enemies<br>with no attunement for 45 seconds every time<br>the dragon gauge fills by 10%. This increase<br>will not stack, and, after activating, this ability<br>will not activate again for five seconds.<\/div><\/dd><\/dl><\/div><\/div><\/div><div><br><\/div><div>\\u30fbThe stats shown here represent the dragon at level 100, maximum bond, and unbound to the fourth stage. They do not represent the stats when first obtained.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>Notes:<\/div><div>1. For more information about summoning, tap Summon on the in-game footer menu, then select Showcase Info and check the Details tab.<\/div><div>2. Alberian Battle Royale skins for the adventurers featured in this summon showcase are on sale and cost fewer items to unlock. Note that some adventurers do not have adventurer skins.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost.<\/div>","start_time":1644818400,"prev_article_id":"2821","next_article_id":"2841","image_path":"","update_time":1644457118}}}'